msgstr "Assicurati di:"

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:52
msgid "Install and activate the WooCommerce plugin"
msgstr "Installare e attivare il plugin WooCommerce"

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:53
msgid ""
"Configure your desired payment gateways in WooCommerce → Settings → Payments"
msgstr ""
"Configura i gateway di pagamento desiderati in WooCommerce -> Impostazioni "
"-> Pagamenti"

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:54
msgid "Set up order emails, statuses, and processing rules in WooCommerce"
msgstr "Impostare email ordine, stati e regole di elaborazione in WooCommerce"

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:55
msgid "Use WooCommerce coupons for any discount or promotion logic"
msgstr "Usare i coupon WooCommerce per qualsiasi logica di sconto o promozione"

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:58
msgid ""
"All pricing for Listdom features (like Booking, Claim, Labelize, etc.) must "
"be mapped to WooCommerce products. Orders will be handled by WooCommerce and "
"visible under WooCommerce → Orders."
msgstr ""
"Tutti i prezzi per le funzionalita di Listdom (come Booking, Claim, "
"Labelize, ecc.) devono essere associati a prodotti WooCommerce. Gli ordini "
"saranno gestiti da WooCommerce e visibili in WooCommerce -> Ordini."

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:59
msgid ""
"You can switch to Listdom's internal payment system at any time if you "
"prefer a lightweight alternative without WooCommerce."
msgstr ""
"Puoi passare in qualsiasi momento al sistema di pagamento interno di Listdom "
"se preferisci un'alternativa leggera senza WooCommerce."

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:65
msgid "Listdom Payment Engine"
msgstr "Motore di pagamento Listdom"

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:67
msgid ""
"In this mode, Listdom handles all payments directly — no need to install or "
"configure WooCommerce."
msgstr ""
"In questa modalita, Listdom gestisce tutti i pagamenti direttamente: non e "
"necessario installare o configurare WooCommerce."

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:71
msgid ""
"Choose and enable your desired payment gateways in Listdom → Settings → "
"Payments"
msgstr ""
"Scegli e abilita i gateway di pagamento desiderati in Listdom -> "
"Impostazioni -> Pagamenti"

#: app/html/menus/settings/tabs/payments.php:72
msgid "Configure manual payment instructions (for On-Site and Wire Transfer)"
msgstr ""
"Configura le istruzioni di pagamento manuale (per On-Site e bonifico "
"bancario)"

